Detailed Description

Base class used to build multiwindow launcher.

MultiWindow launcher is composed by

  • LauncherTray
  • HandleBar
  • Edit Panel It need to imherited this base class. It could be pull the handle bar to move the launcher w/
  • HandleBar only
  • HandleBar + LauncherTray
  • Full screen mode
